74, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"horse-racing\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to 40,000 spectators could attend.\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Up to 40,000 spectators\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like in most pre-industrial societies, life in ancient Greece was deeply physical and a well exercised body was seen as the mark of a gentleman.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4013, \"end\": 4027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999962269612, \"rank\": 3.772844597418164e-09, \"text\": \"ancient Greece\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most pre-industrial societies\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 4003}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"a well exercised body\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4073}, {\"ngram\": \"the mark\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4094}, {\"ngram\": \"a gentleman\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The games continued, with minor blips, until the new Christian authorities in Greece banned them as part of the reprehensible pagan past in 393 AD.\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4165, \"end\": 4174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999791624999299, \"rank\": 0.00020841843007393166, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4190, \"end\": 4196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999983631414334, \"rank\": 1.6368612335618256e-06, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The games\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4121}, {\"ngram\": \"minor blips\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4149}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"the reprehensible pagan\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4243}, {\"ngram\": \"393 AD\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Could anything disrupt the show?\", \"from\": 4261, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4275}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rain.\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rain\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heavy cloud cover.\", \"from\": 4301, \"to\": 4319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Heavy cloud cover\", \"from\": 4301, \"to\": 4318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then the mirror would not work.\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mirror\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But ceremony organisers in Olympia hold several rehearsals in the days leading up to the official lighting, which provide a backup flame should the big day prove sunless.\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4379, \"end\": 4386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.370810198465131e-12, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ceremony organisers\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4375}, {\"ngram\": \"several rehearsals\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4410}, {\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4422}, {\"ngram\": \"the official lighting\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"a backup flame\", \"from\": 4474, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"the big day\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potential protests are a worse headache.\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Potential protests\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4542}, {\"ngram\": \"a worse headache\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice this century - during the lighting ceremonies for the Beijing summer and winter games - human rights activists disrupted the ceremony inside the fenced and heavily-guarded archaeological site.\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lighting ceremonies\", \"from\": 4593, \"to\": 4616}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing summer and winter games\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4656}, {\"ngram\": \"human rights activists\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4681}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4704}, {\"ngram\": \"the fenced and heavily-guarded archaeological site\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even after the embarrassment of the first incident in 2008, Greek police were unable to anticipate and prevent the second, 14 years later.\", \"from\": 4764, \"to\": 4902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4824, \"end\": 4836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellenic_Police\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greek police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellenic_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellenic_Police\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the embarrassment\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4792}, {\"ngram\": \"the first incident\", \"from\": 4796, \"to\": 4814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The flame-lighting, with its broad TV coverage is a magnet for activists who want to grab headlines and even if ancient Olympia can, in theory at least, be efficiently guarded, the route of the torch relay through Greece is too long to be protest-proof.\", \"from\": 4904, \"to\": 5157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5024, \