_Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2008 incidents\", \"from\": 5159, \"to\": 5177}, {\"ngram\": \"the scrapping\", \"from\": 5207, \"to\": 5220}, {\"ngram\": \"the host country\", \"from\": 5256, \"to\": 5272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Further along the road, while the torches are designed to stay lit, there have been hitches in the past.\", \"from\": 5274, \"to\": 5378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 5288, \"to\": 5296}, {\"ngram\": \"the torches\", \"from\": 5304, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"hitches\", \"from\": 5358, \"to\": 5365}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the relay for the 2014 Sochi winter games wind blew out the torch, which was sneakily rekindled with a lighter.\", \"from\": 5380, \"to\": 5498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 5387, \"to\": 5396}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2014 Sochi winter games wind\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 5443, \"to\": 5452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same quick fix was used at Montreal in 1976, when rain extinguished the Olympic cauldron.\", \"from\": 5499, \"to\": 5592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5530, \"end\": 5538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"score\": 0.9999999997776285, \"rank\": 2.0750167196781214e-10, \"text\": \"Montreal\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The same quick fix\", \"from\": 5499, \"to\": 5517}, {\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5557}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic cauldron\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"f